      "post_content": "Turn 1: Forest, Black Lotus, pop for 3 mana, channel 19 life, cast Stream of Life using all 19 channeled mana and the forest for X, gaining you 20 life, putting you at... 21. Best combo ever. ",
      "posted_by": "statiefreez",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost73755\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Turn 1: Forest, Black Lotus, pop for 3 mana, channel 19 life, cast Stream of Life using all 19 channeled mana and the forest for X, gaining you 20 life, putting you at... 21. Best combo ever. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '73755'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy26701\">statiefreez</span>\r\n                                (5/17/2010 7:25:30 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../