    {
      "id": "PopularPost143168",
      "post_content": "\"Thanks, I was TRYING to figure out a way to gain a single life on the first turn.\"  \n  \nAssuming you're on the draw, you could [Forest](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Forest), [Lotus Petal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lotus Petal), crack the petal and tap the forest to gain 1. Or if you're using banned/restricted cards, [Forest](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Forest), [Lotus Petal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lotus Petal), crack the petal, [Mana Vault](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Vault), tap, [Mana Vault](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Vault), [Mana Vault](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Vault), [Mana Vault](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Vault), tap those three for 9 colorless floating, tap the forest and play this for 9 life. (Cut out one Vault if you're on the play.) And then start taking 4 damage per turn.  \n  \nBut personally I like statiefreez's idea of [Channel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Channel)ing 19 more.",
      "posted_by": "Lyoncet",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost143168\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">\"Thanks, I was TRYING to figure out a way to gain a single life on the first turn.\"<br/><br/>Assuming you're on the draw, you could <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Forest\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Forest\">Forest</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lotus Petal\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lotus Petal\">Lotus Petal</a>, crack the petal and tap the forest to gain 1.  Or if you're using banned/restricted cards, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Forest\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Forest\">Forest</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lotus Petal\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lotus Petal\">Lotus Petal</a>, crack the petal, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mana Vault\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Vault\">Mana Vault</a>, tap, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mana Vault\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Vault\">Mana Vault</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mana Vault\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Vault\">Mana Vault</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mana Vault\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Vault\">Mana Vault</a>, tap those three for 9 colorless floating, tap the forest and play this for 9 life.  (Cut out one Vault if you're on the play.)  And then start taking 4 damage per turn.<br/><br/>But personally I like statiefreez's idea of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Channel\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Channel\">Channel</a>ing 19 more.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '143168'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy54409\">Lyoncet</span>\r\n                                (3/11/2011 4:10:27 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
