    {
      "id": "PopularPost212083",
      "post_content": "You know, if you can draw a couple more Black Lotus and a [Sanguine Bond](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sanguine Bond), you can totally turn that Channel trick into a first-turn kill.  \n  \nActually, a ![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)![Green](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=G&type=symbol) deck running Sanguine Bond might be the only thing that might make me use this today, and that's only if I don't just want to keep it black and kill people with [Corrupt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Corrupt). A staple in my decks in my noobier days though.",
      "posted_by": "jfre81",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost212083\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">You know, if you can draw a couple more Black Lotus and a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sanguine Bond\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sanguine Bond\">Sanguine Bond</a>, you can totally turn that Channel trick into a first-turn kill.<br/><br/>Actually, a <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Green\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=G&amp;type=symbol\"/> deck running Sanguine Bond might be the only thing that might make me use this today, and that's only if I don't just want to keep it black and kill people with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Corrupt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Corrupt\">Corrupt</a>. A staple in my decks in my noobier days though.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '212083'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy59706\">jfre81</span>\r\n                                (11/18/2011 2:17:28 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                    